{"tid":156404,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美女與野獸背後的意義","createTime":"2017-03-14T16:48:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-24T17:10:07.000Z","uid":34286,"like":531,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6747f2d9f3e43230fcee6cad40910993ad924ebb","tid":156404,"uid":34286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T16:48:51.000Z","msg":"野獸其實不是重點<br />\n野獸擁有古堡(等同現時的豪宅)和擁有名貴的東西(即是有錢)<br />\n如果野獸又無豪宅, 又無錢, 只是一個住山洞的流浪獸, 故事會發生嗎?<br />\n<br />\n又掉轉來講, 如果美女, 不是美女. 怪獸會選擇她嗎?<br />\n<br />\n根本這個迪士尼告訴大家, 一切都很現實<br />\n男方要有樓有錢, 女方要靚<br />\n說到底, 呢個只係一個條件交易, 而不是愛情"},{"pid":"1f061079fceef5a2e79acede89f254113aa1661a","tid":156404,"uid":13444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T16:52:05.000Z","msg":"從來世界都係咁<br />\n係從來"},{"pid":"acff18a50e7455450efb3b095af5d9fd96b055a9","tid":156404,"uid":34286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T16:52:28.000Z","msg":"為什麼不可以是醜女與野獸<br />\n<br />\n甚至是醜女與怪獸, 醜女與異形<br />\n<br />\n講到底, 就係條件交易"},{"pid":"83142c3699fd3fbfae0e15932e3665e8a110e8f3","tid":156404,"uid":12421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T16:53:00.000Z","msg":"駁唔到..."},{"pid":"dc171f9965174acf2c265e56a20e979104aa8dfe","tid":156404,"uid":25086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T16:54:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/15/005403_ca33120d9c7577bd348327c66a2f20c5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F15%2F005403_ca33120d9c7577bd348327c66a2f20c5.jpg&h=1b5154e1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cf328f5032c571304b95b9047baf378119d0389e","tid":156404,"uid":3558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T16:54:20.000Z","msg":"其實可能係人獸交"},{"pid":"18d274a0ae3ad2659bfc21eb5b7ac596f3692b2a","tid":156404,"uid":51796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T16:55:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實可能係人獸交</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae0456be5d01f67cb248f1c383e5efc4187ea8aa","tid":156404,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T16:56:32.000Z","msg":"野獸本身係王子黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a9b82d26c3fb71eddc48949e23273b51f7325ca","tid":156404,"uid":34286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T16:57:34.000Z","msg":"有時, 看超人拯救地球<br />\n<br />\n為什麼不可以是殘疾人仕感化地球入侵者之進化版異形"},{"pid":"76fa4f96a11abaf0942d2f11e25841224cc54728","tid":156404,"uid":34286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T16:59:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>野獸本身係王子黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咪一撚樣, 即係件港女, 諗住博埋野獸變番王子, 賺到盡<br />\n如果唔變番王子, 都起碼有錢有樓渣手, 無得輸<br />\n<br />\n進可攻退可守"},{"pid":"c0573a825c7cd71410960f28667c9661d0ac1528","tid":156404,"uid":31796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T17:02:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>野獸本身係王子黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咪一撚樣, 即係件港女, 諗住博埋野獸變番王子, 賺到盡<br />\n如果唔變番王子, 都起碼有錢有樓渣手, 無得輸<br />\n<br />\n進可攻退可守</blockquote><br />\n仲要仆街到賣左個老豆去大富豪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0f1afe670969737ba0022e22d1086ad94f57e7b","tid":156404,"uid":45591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T17:03:18.000Z","msg":"Yes,即使個美女有口臭都冇所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"065445ab18d39b59ab6e6b7281d4561613a8d204","tid":156404,"uid":78253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T17:06:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>為什麼不可以是醜女與野獸<br />\n<br />\n甚至是醜女與怪獸, 醜女與異形<br />\n<br />\n講到底, 就係條件交易</blockquote><br />\n醜女與野獸==&gt;史力加, 好正"},{"pid":"40b76d7aba