me":"2017-03-15T02:08:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇史力加先有意義</blockquote><br />\n佢應該係唯一套，但佢成套野基本上都反童話咁做，又幾好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9e1a81d98f38d8c19bea625cd7faeb4ef78b00d","tid":156404,"uid":91326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T02:09:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁青蛙王子呢？</blockquote><br />\n咪又撚係王子<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76cf4def045c497ce84de208f879b74de07e3587","tid":156404,"uid":21222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T02:11:26.000Z","msg":"迪士尼不嬲係公主病既主腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaeaea4068ccea222124aff88edd2cbb726d1572","tid":156404,"uid":44036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T02:30:41.000Z","msg":"史力加唔係迪士尼架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"037b268d705802ef2cf709d568a607c6cc85beab","tid":156404,"uid":43678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T02:34:57.000Z","msg":"屎力加都唔係迪士尼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過好睇好多"},{"pid":"db5cf1bddd7fd6142794b52ec91ddaeb799124cf","tid":156404,"uid":3647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T02:37:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>野獸本身係王子黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咪一撚樣, 即係件港女, 諗住博埋野獸變番王子, 賺到盡<br />\n如果唔變番王子, 都起碼有錢有樓渣手, 無得輸<br />\n<br />\n進可攻退可守</blockquote><br />\n仲要仆街到賣左個老豆去大富豪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n用五隻雞就可以換到老豆</blockquote><br />\n仲有燒鵝</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n幾多年前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></bloc