assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n家陣唔係一般人搭一般人 係極好package配極好package <br />\n<br />\n一開始咪問咁若果野獸只係住山洞 重會唔會有美女？<br />\n我夠膽答就算唔係山洞 係一間正常但普通嘅屋 都唔會有女睇得上</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n普通人咪配返普通人囉<br />\n有乜問題？<br />\n<br />\n男無樓無錢，但想娶個樣靚身材正老婆？<br />\n女嘅又肥又樣衰，但想嫁個有錢佬唔洗做？<br />\n你咁想有個完美伴侶，不如努力增值自己<br />\n唔好自己無樣好，就幻想有個靚女會同你一齊捱"},{"pid":"29454180ee0fc15e6eb2c367c52bdbf0edc5d031","tid":156404,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T03:29:38.000Z","msg":"女權：物化女性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fae6fdd8d140dc13252c18812f7e092e327e9ddb","tid":156404,"uid":5293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T03:36:25.000Z","msg":"泰山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd3b00e808f9712737b0e91f21aa95747d9713fb","tid":156404,"uid":54137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T03:38:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>野獸本身係王子黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咪一撚樣, 即係件港女, 諗住博埋野獸變番王子, 賺到盡<br />\n如果唔變番王子, 都起碼有錢有樓渣手, 無得輸<br />\n<br />\n進可攻退可守</blockquote><br />\n仲要仆街到賣左個老豆去大富豪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n用五隻雞就可以換到老豆</blockquote><br />\n仲有燒鵝</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n幾多年前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n聽講老豆係想去大富豪 佢去既係中國城</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6FjtBUctLEU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6FjtBUctLEU&d=m%2FBV6vIUiVByATU953Ynm